【新圍 CBS】Sacramento City Council Approves Ban On Flavored Tobacco Products
美國沙加緬度市（SacramentoCity）市議會修法通過~禁售所有加味菸!美國癌症協會（AmericanCancerSociety)副主席JimKnox指出「電子煙是具高度濃縮的尼古丁產品，不會讓你脫離尼古丁，反而會讓你沉迷於尼古丁」。美國政府在一開始未嚴格管理電子煙，2018年已有超過360萬名中學生使用電子煙，僅在一年內增加了150萬，高中生的電子煙使用率就提高了78％，有如傳染病般迅速影響。#專家說每一位戒菸者使用電子煙戒菸，同時導致80個青少年開始使用電子煙#新法將於明年1月1日開始執行#感謝台大醫院家庭醫學部醫師郭斐然醫師指導-------------------------------------------------------------------SacramentoCityCouncilApprovesBanOnFlavoredTobaccoProductsByRachelWulffApril16,2019at7:26pmFiledUnder:FlavoredTobacco,SacramentoCityCouncil,Smoking,teens,vapingSACRAMENTO(CBS13)—TheSacramentoCityCouncilhasapprovedabanonallflavoredtobaccoproductsinthecitylimits.Therearecurrently400licensesforthesetypesofsalesinthecityatvapeshops,gasstations,grocerystores,andwineandliquorstores.Anti-smokingexpertssayflavoredtobaccoproductsarethegatewaytotobaccoproductsandhighlyaddictive.Theownerofonelocalshopwillbeatthatmeetingtonight.Hesaysthesetypesofproductsarehislivelihoodandbanningthenwillputhimoutofbusiness.Anti-smokinggroupssayithastobedonetoblockaccessforteens.HeatherBeckhamhasa17-year-oldsonwho’salreadyfamiliarwithvaping.“Bothofmygrandfathersdiedfromlungcancerandheknowsalloftheusefulinformationandhecanwalkintoanybathroomoncampusandgetane-cigarette.It’sreallydisheartening,”Beckhamsaid.ShesupportsaproposedbanonallflavoredtobaccoproductsinthecityofSacramentoandsheisworkingwiththeAmericanCancerSociety’scanceractionnetworktoinformpeopleabouttheproblem.“E-cigaretteusageinhighstudentsisup78percentinoneyearalone.TheFDAiscallingthisanepidemicandweknowit’sthreateningdecadesofprogressinreducingsmokingrates,”saidJimKnox,VicePresidentoftheAmericanCancerSociety.TheFDAsays80percentofsmokersstartedwithaflavoredtobaccoproduct.ButNoorddinKacchisaystheyaren’tgettingitfromhim.KacchirunsCloudNineSmokeandVapeshopinNatomas,hesaid85%ofhisbusinessisfromsalesofflavoredliquidproductsandhardwarefore-cigarettesandvaping.“I’mnotevensurewe’regoingtobeinbusinessifthisflavorbangetsapproved,”Kacchhisaid.Hesaysvapingisahealthieralternativeforlong-timesmokerslikeAustinSorensen,w